longBusinessSummary: International Endeavors Corp creates, manufactures, and markets technology for the cannabis industry. It focuses on building patented technology that supports the rapid deployment of agricultural infrastructure and the equipment needed for the medical marijuana and legal cannabis industry. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Temecula, California.
